    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the clerical fanon garment as worn from the late twelfth century onward, when it was worn solely by the pope, as decreed by Pope Innocent III. The papal vestment was originally called an "orale," but later became known as a "fanon orale." The present collar-like form of the garment appeared in the sixteenth century or later.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079245/Catholic Encyclopedia [online] (2003-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Religieuze kapmantel die vanaf de late twaalfde eeuw, vanwege een decreet van paus Innocentius III, alleen door pausen mocht worden gedragen. Dit pauselijke gewaad noemde men oorspronkelijk een 'orale', maar later een 'fanon orale'. Het huidige ontwerp met kraag verscheen in de zestiende eeuw of daarna.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元十二世紀後期迄今，根據教宗依諾森三世所頒布之命令，僅限由教宗穿戴的圓領布。此種教宗所穿的祭服原本稱為「歐拉邊巾」（orale），後來才改稱為「歐拉圓領布」（或「教宗圓領布」）。現今該服裝如衣領般的形式係於十六世紀或更晚期才出現。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
